<P>BY EDWARD BRAILSFORD, OF CHARLESTON, SOUTH-CAROLINA, MEMBER OF THE MEDICAL AND CHEMICAL SOCIETIES OF PHILADELPHIA.</P>
<P>PHILADELPHIA: PRINTED BY <HI>JOHN ORMROD,</HI> N^o. 41, CHESNUT STREET.</P>
